    "en": {
      "name": "Eosvarog, Forger of the Dawn",
      "effect": "2 LIGHT Machine monsters\nIf this card is Fusion Summoned: You can activate this effect; during the Standby Phase of the next turn, add 1 card from your GY to your hand with an effect that Fusion Summons. When your opponent activates a Spell/Trap Card or effect (Quick Effect): You can banish 1 face-up LIGHT Machine monster you control OR 2 LIGHT Machine monsters from your GY; negate the activation. You can only use each effect of \"Eosvarog, Forger of the Dawn\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
